com.missing.inspect
Interface InspectorRenderer

public interface InspectorRenderer

The InspectorRenderer is an interface for classes which can serve to influence the output of inspector. Consider simple classes like Point or your own, you might not want to have them printed out in a verbose way such as toString does.
